    "title": "Formstack: Automate Forms, Docs & E-Signatures Fast",
    "excerpt": "Formstack turns messy paperwork into automated workflows with smart forms, doc generation, and e-signatures. See how it saves teams hours weekly.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/what-is-formstack.jpg",
