    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I have a confession: I used to spend entire afternoons chasing signatures, retyping data from PDFs, and building clunky Google Forms that broke on mobile. Then I found Formstack — and honestly, it felt like hiring three assistants for the price of a software subscription.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you deal with intake forms, client onboarding, contract signing, or any repetitive document process, this post is for you. I'm going to break down exactly what Formstack is, what makes it different, and why thousands of organizations from nonprofits to Fortune 500 companies swear by it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I'll also share some recent updates that make it even more powerful in 2025. Let's get into it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Is Formstack?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://intellistack.partnerlinks.io/mhua7fhknizd"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Formstack",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " is a no-code automation platform built around three core pillars: ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "digital forms",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "document generation",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", and ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "electronic signatures",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". Think of it as a unified workspace where data flows from the moment someone fills out a form all the way to a signed, filed document — without anyone touching paper or copying information by hand.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform launched in 2006 as a simple form builder. Since then, it has evolved into a full workflow automation suite trusted by organizations like Cleveland Clinic, Netflix, and PayPal. What I appreciate most is that Formstack didn't just bolt on features randomly. Each piece — Forms, Documents, and Sign — connects natively, so data captured in a form automatically populates a contract template and routes it for signature.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "No code. No duct-tape integrations. Just workflows that actually work.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://intellistack.partnerlinks.io/mhua7fhknizd"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You can explore the full feature set and ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "try Formstack free for 14 days",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". There's no credit card required, which I always appreciate.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Standout Features That Set Formstack Apart",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've tested dozens of form builders and document automation tools. Here's what makes Formstack stand out in a crowded market.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Smart Logic Forms",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Formstack's conditional logic is genuinely impressive. You can build forms that adapt in real time based on what someone selects. If a respondent picks \"Business Plan\" as their inquiry type, the form shows relevant follow-up questions. If they pick \"Support,\" it shows different ones entirely. This means cleaner data, shorter forms, and higher completion rates.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I built a client intake form with 12 conditional branches in about 20 minutes. Try doing that in a basic form builder without losing your mind.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Document Generation",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is where Formstack really shines for sales teams, legal departments, and HR. You design a document template once — a proposal, an employment contract, a waiver — and Formstack pulls data directly from your form submissions to auto-populate every field.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "No more copy-pasting client names. No more forgetting to update a date. The data flows from the form into the document automatically.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-formstack"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You can read a deeper walkthrough on ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "how to use Formstack for document workflows",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Native E-Signatures",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Formstack Sign is built into the platform, not a third-party add-on. Send documents for signature via email, track who's opened and signed, and store completed documents — all inside Formstack. Signatures are legally binding and compliant with U.S. ESIGN Act and UETA standards.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What I love: you can set signing order. Send a contract to Client A first, then automatically route it to your manager once Client A signs. Zero manual handoffs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "200+ Integrations",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Formstack connects with Salesforce, Google Sheets, Slack, Microsoft Teams, Stripe, PayPal, HubSpot, and over 200 other tools through native integrations and connectors like Zapier. Data captured in a form can trigger a Slack notification, create a Salesforce lead, and add a row to a Google Sheet — simultaneously.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This integration depth is what separates Formstack from simpler alternatives. It doesn't just collect data; it pushes data everywhere you need it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Workspaces and Collaboration",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Formstack supports team workspaces where departments can manage their own forms and templates while staying within your organization's account. Admins get centralized billing and user management. Each team gets independence without chaos.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-formstack"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you want a deeper dive into these capabilities, check out our guide on ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
