        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Form data auto-populates a service agreement.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Using Formstack Documents, your pre-built contract template pulls the client's name, company, selected services, and pricing tier directly from the form. The document is generated in seconds.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Contract routes for signature.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Formstack Sign sends the auto-generated agreement to the client via email. They review and sign on any device. Once signed, it automatically routes to your managing partner for counter-signature.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Notifications fire everywhere.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " A Slack message hits your #new-clients channel. A new row appears in your client tracking Google Sheet. A Salesforce opportunity moves to \"Closed Won.\"",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "5. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Signed document stores automatically.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The completed, signed agreement saves to your preferred cloud storage — Google Drive, Dropbox, or SharePoint.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Five steps. Zero paper. Zero manual data entry. What used to take your admin 45 minutes now takes zero minutes of human time.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
