    "image_prompt": "Editorial tech thumbnail, 16:9. Incorporate the brand logo fetched from https://logo.clearbit.com/formstack.com as the clean focal element over a soft amber-to-cream gradient (Notion + Apple aesthetic). A busy office desk transforming into a clean, paperless digital workspace with floating form fields and a glowing signature icon on a laptop screen. Glassmorphism cards, soft volumetric light, generous negative space for a title, no embedded text, no watermark. --ar 16:9 --style raw",
    "faq_items": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What is Formstack used for?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Formstack is used for automating data collection with digital forms, generating documents from form data, and collecting legally binding electronic signatures. It replaces manual, paper-based workflows with no-code automated processes across industries like healthcare, sales, HR, legal, and education.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Formstack free?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Formstack offers a 14-day free trial with full access to its features — no credit card required. After the trial, paid plans start at $83/month billed annually for Formstack Forms. There is no permanent free tier, but the trial gives you enough time to evaluate whether it fits your needs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Formstack secure and compliant?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Formstack is SOC 2 Type II compliant, supports HIPAA-eligible configurations for healthcare use cases, and complies with U.S. ESIGN Act and UETA standards for electronic signatures. Enterprise plans include SSO, audit trails, and enhanced encryption.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can Formstack integrate with Salesforce?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. Formstack has a native Salesforce integration that supports bi-directional data sync. You can push form data into Salesforce records, pre-fill forms using existing Salesforce data, and trigger workflows based on Salesforce events.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
